item.dc:creator: @magep00ner12 magep00ner12
item.description:
@magep00ner12 wrote:

[quote=“azz4eva, post:2, topic:6432”]On hamachi click the triangle thing click create a new network it will say network name in the top white box type the name of your server in then in the other box (under it type 123 thats your password people need to know it so 123 is simple)

for people to get on click run.bat and leave it on for people if you close it it crashes moparscape (use silab it has skillcapes and stuff) or use moparscape

You dont need No-Ip for your server if you have hamachi.[/quote]
